        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_watch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 900
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_watch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1500
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_watch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1800
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "これは……『カセットテープ』？\n他はハイテクなのにこれだけ古いのね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… a “cassette tape”?\nEverything else is high-tech‚ yet this alone is so old…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666587,
      "endTime": 10.394694097799999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 6.9333333254
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 10.6013605356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　みんな、見て下さい！　パラレルトラベルマシン\nの中にラジカセがあります！　これに入れれば……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! Everyone‚ look! There’s a radio-cassette player\ninside the Parallel Travel Machine! If we put it in here…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6013605356,
      "endTime": 19.066669329,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3600.0000078999983
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 17.1999999921
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 20.4906822127
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは……！　魚魚っとさん音頭だわ！　くっ……\n体が勝手に……歌いたくないのに口ずさんでしまうわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-this is…! It’s Gyogyo-tto-san Ondo! Ugh…\nMy body’s moving on its own… I don’t want to sing it‚ but I’m humming along…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4906822127,
      "endTime": 31.9242195052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 32.1308860383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ぎょぎょっとぎょぎょっと今日も～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyo-tto‚ Gyogyo-tto‚ and today~‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1308860383,
      "endTime": 34.5751603048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ぎょぎょっとぎょぎょっと踊れ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyo-tto‚ Gyogyo-tto‚ let's dance~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5751603048,
      "endTime": 37.166667429600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 37.3011587064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、みんなどうしちゃったの！？　その変な\n踊りは何！？　これもザグラ達の罠……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ what’s gotten into everyone!? What’s with that weird dance!?\nIs this another trap by Zagura and the others…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3011587064,
      "endTime": 45.3380528371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 45.5513861895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "違いますわ！　私達星見市民は魚魚っとさん音頭を\n聞くと体が勝手に動いてしまうんですの～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it’s not! We citizens of Hoshimi—when we hear\nthe Gyogyo-tto-san Ondo‚ our bodies just start moving on their own~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5513861895,
      "endTime": 54.071272969300004,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_machine-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9666.553465599996
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9899.888833399998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　見て下さい！　パラレルトラベルマシンに乗って\nいる魚魚っとさんが動き出しました……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! Look! The Gyogyo-tto-san riding\non the Parallel Travel Machine has started moving…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3179429611,
      "endTime": 63.10494914860001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "は！？　なんで魚魚っとさん音頭踊ったら\n起動するんだよ！　どういう世界観だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? Why does dancing the Gyogyo-tto-san Ondo\nmake it start up!? What kind of world logic is that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3116159679,
      "endTime": 70.023543191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "きっと運転席に乗っている魚魚っとさんもマシンの\n一部で、最後のカギになっていたのよ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyo-tto-san sitting in the driver’s seat must also be\npart of the machine—and the final key…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2368763527,
      "endTime": 77.4902321419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "魚魚っとさん、パラレルワールドでも凄く\n愛されてるんだね！　嬉しいギョ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyo-tto-san is really loved\neven in the parallel world! That makes me happy‚ gyo~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7035654944,
      "endTime": 85.5971257133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、これで帰れますわよ！\nさぁ、パラレルトラベルマシンに乗るのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now we can go home!\nCome on‚ let’s board the Parallel Travel Machine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7837925515,
      "endTime": 92.8795746406,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2888.4287516999902
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7295.781993800006
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、乗船確認！\nそれじゃ……星見プロに、しゅっぱーつ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All right‚ boarding check!\nThen… departing for Hoshimi Pro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0795745453,
      "endTime": 100.2795743546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "待って！　時空の狭間の入り口が……どんどん\n閉じていってる！　このままじゃ、間に合わない……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait! The entrance to the space-time rift is…\nclosing more and more! At this rate‚ we won’t make it…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2929076117,
      "endTime": 109.7651755255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 101.6655558824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "絶体絶命よ！　どうすればいいの……！？\nもう、星見プロへは帰れないの……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re in a hopeless situation! What should we do…!?\nAre we… never going back to Hoshimi Pro…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9585088016,
      "endTime": 116.906558633,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7134.716669799999
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7134.716669799999
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_machine-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7134.716669799999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-gyogyo001.m4a",
      "text": "いつもみんなのそばに～\nギョギョっと現れる～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Always by everyone’s side~\nappearing with a Gyogyo-tto~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.0932254714,
      "endTime": 126.39728186129999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "マシンが急加速した……！？　見て！　沢山の小さい\n魚魚っとさんが後ろからマシンを押してくれてるわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The machine suddenly accelerated…!? Look! Lots of tiny\nGyogyo-tto-sans are pushing the machine from behind!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4582847836,
      "endTime": 134.18359110379998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "奇跡……奇跡が起こったわ……！\n魚魚っとさん達も応援してくれているのね……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A miracle… a miracle just happened…!\nThe Gyogyo-tto-sans are cheering us on too…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3969241701,
      "endTime": 140.66513295989998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "なんなんだよこのノリ！　魚魚っとさんって\n何者だよ！？　あーもう、とにかく行けー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is with this vibe!? Who even\nis Gyogyo-tto-san!? Ugh‚ whatever—just go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8517997983,
      "endTime": 147.8025843541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "わあぁぁぁ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waaaahhh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8414587262,
      "endTime": 149.26925712419998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "大変よ！　遙子がマシンから落ちそうだわ！\nそれより、なんでそんな所から身を乗り出しているのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is bad! Haruko’s about to fall off the machine!\nMore importantly‚ why are you leaning out from there!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3078357143,
      "endTime": 156.34386743730002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_05-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "だ、だって、眺めがいいかなと思って……！　みんな\n私のことは置いて行って！　サクリファイスよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I thought the view might be nice…! Everyone‚\njust leave me behind! I’ll be the sacrifice!",
